,"text_bw":"badarato minohu bawaAdiru gDabK","text_ar":"بَدَرَتْ مِنْهُ بَوَادِرُ غضَبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badarat bawaAdiru","text_ar":"بَدَرَت بَوَادِرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxayoli","text_ar":"الخَيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdirapN","text_ar":"بَادِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badarati AlA_ibila","text_ar":"بَدَرَتِ الاـِبِلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought forth at an earlier period of the year than the other camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badoriy~apN","text_ar":"بَدْرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badoriY~N","text_ar":"بَدْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarajotu A^aboduru","text_ar":"خَرَجْتُ اَبْدُرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I went forth to make water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n1979","headword_ar":"بَدْرٌ","root":"bdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K, &c.,) originally an inf. n., (Msb,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full moon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdirN","text_ar":"بَادِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, K;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moon in its fourteenth night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or the latter signifies [simply] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T:) the moon in its fourteenth night is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bdr","text_ar":"بدر"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it hastens to rise before the sun sets; (S, M;) and to set before the sun rises: (TA:) or because of its fulness; (S, TA;) as being likened to a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badorap","text_ar":"بَدْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as Er-Rághib thinks to be most probable, it is itself a primitive word: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buduwrN","text_ar":"بُدُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, A.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapu Albadori","text_ar":"لَيْلَةُ البَدْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night of the full moon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fourteenth night"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the lunar month"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lord, master,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) of a people: so called as being likened to the full moon. (M.) ―         -b3-  Applied to a boy, (Zj, M, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Full of youthful vigour and of flesh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plump:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mubaAdirN","text_ar":"مُبَادِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precocious"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T, K.) [In this sense, an epithet; and so its fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badorapN","text_ar":"بَدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.), applied to an eye.] ―         -b4-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cover;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dish"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plate;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaqN","text_ar":"طَبَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ibn-Wahb, K:) because resembling the full moon, being round: so Az thinks. (TA.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badorapN","text_ar":"بَدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in 